## Guidelines
- xUnit `[Fact]`, `[Theory]`/`[InlineData]`
- Naming: `Method_Condition_ExpectedResult`
- Arrange-Act-Assert
- `#nullable enable`, namespace `ContosoUniversity.Tests.Controllers`
- Create fresh context per test
- Complete, compilable code — no placeholders
- For ViewBag assertions, use `((ViewResult)result).ViewData["key"]` or cast controller.ViewBag dynamically
- For JsonResult: `var jsonResult = result as JsonResult; Assert.NotNull(jsonResult);` then check `.Value` properties using reflection or dynamic
